You can easily download SNES Romset Ultra for free.

https://urlis.net/tw235vey

As others have pointed out, the torrent stalls at 99.6% - but, there are only three files which fail to download, and two of those are database files.

It also doesn't contain the ROMs in the "Extras" folder - various Virtual Console ROMs - you can find that folder by clicking "SHOW ALL" under Download Options, it's at the top of the list.

The one broken ROM in the torrent is "Yume Meikyuu - Kigurumi Daibouken" - you can download it manually from the list of files in the archive.

Also - I manually downloaded the broken files, moved them to the torrent's download folder and forced a recheck in qBittorrent and they weren't marked as downloaded, so there's a checksum error and the torrent will remain broken unless it's repaired by the uploader.
